About Reel Sound Studios
Reel Sound Studios is a recording studio focused on professionalism, hospitality, musicality, and creativity. We want you to not only feel comfortable but that your song will come out even better than you imagined. With two studio rooms, both equipped with great microphones, top of the line gear and amazing engineers to use them, we assure you this is the place to record your hit.

Our Team
Meet the Reel Sound Studios team.
J. Reelz
Owner, Recording Engineer
Jason (J. Reelz) is the owner, manager and lead engineer of Reel Sound Studios. Jason has been immersed in music since he was a child, learning the keyboard at the age of 7 until joining his high school marching band’s drumline. From there he was awarded a full scholarship to the Miami International University of Art and Design to study Audio Production. Since graduating Jason has worked at a number of studios and worked with many artists and producers until founding Reel Sound Studios in 2020.
Instagram
Envelope
Jennica
Recording Engineer
Jennica has always been musically inclined. She has developed skills through various musical avenues through the years. Her ability to sing makes her an asset to any singer songwriter that she works with. She is also self taught in multiple instruments and looking forward to furthering her engineering experience here at reel sound studios.
Instagram
Mike Anthem
Recording Engineer
Mike Anthem brings more than 10 years of experience to the table, specializing in live sound, production, mixing, and engineering. His style is influenced by his upbringing in Queens, NY. Mike has worked with artists such as Trabass, Gabby Queem, philly Mae, Jack Boy, and more.
Instagram
Envelope
Josiah the Messiah
Recording Engineer
Josiah The Messiah has more than 5 years of experience in engineering. He went to the Berklee College of Music and studied CWP (contemporary writing and production) and music business. Josiah also creates beats through his label, Diversounds.
Instagram
Envelope
Khai Genius
Recording Engineer
Ahmad Hosein (professionally known as Khai Genius) is a professional musician, recording engineer, and producer based out of Miami Gardens, FL. Influenced heavily by Hip Hop and R&B, Khai has worked with both indie and major label artists within both genres. His main focus when working on any artist is getting the absolute best out of them, pulling out the musical ability that he/she didn’t realize they had.
Instagram
Ceemorr Bandz
Producer
Ceemorr Bandz has been producing music since the age of 14. He is known for his  musical storytelling and creative melodies. The Bronx-born and Miami-raised engineer has produced for artists like Ace Hood and Trabass.
Instagram
Envelope
John Lainez
Recording Engineer
Broward county native, John Lainez has always had a passion for music. After charting #38 on SoundCloud in 2017, he switched his focus from rapping to writing, production, and engineering. His credits include Wifisfuneral and Big Baby Gucci.
